  • Classes in com.badlogic.gdx.ai.pfa used by com.badlogic.gdx.ai.pfa 
    Class and Description
    Connection
    A connection between two nodes of the Graph.
    Graph
    A graph is a collection of nodes, each one having a collection of outgoing connections.
    GraphPath
    A GraphPath represents a path in a Graph.
    Heuristic
    A Heuristic generates estimates of the cost to move from a given node to the goal.
    HierarchicalGraph
    A HierarchicalGraph is a multilevel graph that can be traversed by a HierarchicalPathFinder at any level of its hierarchy.
    PathFinder
    A PathFinder that can find a path from one node in an arbitrary graph to a goal node based on information provided by that graph.
    PathFinderRequest
    A request for interruptible pathfinding that should be sent to a PathFinderQueue through a Telegram.
    PathSmootherRequest
    A request for interruptible path smoothing.
    SmoothableGraphPath
    A path that can be smoothed by a PathSmoother.
